    <item>
      <title>巴拿马债券上涨，交易员欢呼亲市场穆利诺的胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/panama-bonds-jump-as-traders-cheer-mulino-s-pro-business-stance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[何塞·劳尔·穆利诺 (Jose Raul Mulino) 赢得总统大选并在胜选演讲中承诺组建“支持私营企业”的政府后，巴拿马政府债券成为周一拉丁美洲涨幅最大的债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/panama-bonds-jump-as-traders-cheer-mulino-s-pro-business-stance</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 14:25:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Arini 等债权人将接管贝恩资本的 Consolis</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/bain-capital-to-hand-precast-concrete-firm-consolis-to-creditors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[包括对冲基金 Arini 在内的债权人将从贝恩资本手中接管 Consolis，作为削减这家建筑材料公司 3 亿欧元（3.23 亿美元）净债务的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/bain-capital-to-hand-precast-concrete-firm-consolis-to-creditors</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 09:16:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
